    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Setup ganglia monitoring on your Amazon EC2 clusters]]></title>
    <link href="http://notes.mindprince.in/2013/11/23/setup-ganglia-monitoring-on-your-amazon-ec2-clusters.html"/>
    <updated>2013-11-23T13:54:00+05:30</updated>
    <id>http://notes.mindprince.in/2013/11/23/setup-ganglia-monitoring-on-your-amazon-ec2-clusters</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>I started four instances running <code>Amazon Linux AMI 2013.09.1 - ami-4296c310 (64-bit)</code> in the Singapore region <code>ap-southeast-1</code>. The security group for these instances allowed inbound SSH and HTTP from my IP address and all traffic from other instances in the same security group.</p>

<h2>ON THE MASTER INSTANCE</h2>

<h3>Installation</h3>

<p>Install <code>ganglia-gmond</code>, <code>ganglia-gmetad</code> and <code>ganglia-web</code>.</p>

<pre><code>sudo yum install ganglia-gmond ganglia-gmetad ganglia-web
</code></pre>

<h3>Edit <code>ganglia</code> configuration files</h3>

<pre><code>sudo vim /etc/ganglia/gmond.conf 
</code></pre>

<p><div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
<span class='line-number'>7</span>
<span class='line-number'>8</span>
<span class='line-number'>9</span>
<span class='line-number'>10</span>
<span class='line-number'>11</span>
<span class='line-number'>12</span>
<span class='line-number'>13</span>
<span class='line-number'>14</span>
<span class='line-number'>15</span>
<span class='line-number'>16</span>
<span class='line-number'>17</span>
<span class='line-number'>18</span>
<span class='line-number'>19</span>
<span class='line-number'>20</span>
<span class='line-number'>21</span>
<span class='line-number'>22</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>.
</span><span class='line'>.
</span><span class='line'>cluster {
</span><span class='line'>  name = &ldquo;ganglia-test&rdquo;
</span><span class='line'>  .
</span><span class='line'>  .
</span><span class='line'>}&lt;/p>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>&lt;p>udp_send_channel {
</span><span class='line'>  host = PRIVATE.IP.ADDRESS.MASTER
</span><span class='line'>  port = 8649
</span><span class='line'>}&lt;/p>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>&lt;p>udp_recv_channel {
</span><span class='line'>  port = 8649
</span><span class='line'>}&lt;/p>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>&lt;p>tcp_accept_channel {
</span><span class='line'>  port = 8649
</span><span class='line'>}
</span><span class='line'>.
</span><span class='line'>.</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div></p>

<pre><code>sudo vim /etc/ganglia/gmetad.conf 
</code></pre>

<p><div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>.
</span><span class='line'>.
</span><span class='line'>data_source &ldquo;ganglia-test‚Äù PRIVATE.IP.ADDRESS.MASTER
</span><span class='line'>.
</span><span class='line'>.</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div></p>

<h3>Edit apache httpd configuration files</h3>

<pre><code>sudo vim /etc/httpd/conf/httpd.conf  
</code></pre>

<p><div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
<span class='line-number'>7</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>.
</span><span class='line'>.
</span><span class='line'>&lt;Directory "/usr/share/ganglia">
</span><span class='line'>  Require all granted
</span><span class='line'>&lt;/Directory>
</span><span class='line'>.
</span><span class='line'>.</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div></p>

<pre><code>sudo vim /etc/httpd/conf.d/ganglia.conf 
</code></pre>

<p><div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
<span class='line-number'>7</span>
<span class='line-number'>8</span>
<span class='line-number'>9</span>
<span class='line-number'>10</span>
<span class='line-number'>11</span>
<span class='line-number'>12</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>.
</span><span class='line'>.
</span><span class='line'>Alias /ganglia /usr/share/ganglia&lt;/p>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>&lt;p>&lt;Location /ganglia>
</span><span class='line'>  Order deny,allow
</span><span class='line'>  Allow from all
</span><span class='line'>  Allow from 127.0.0.1
</span><span class='line'>  Allow from ::1
</span><span class='line'>&lt;/Location>
</span><span class='line'>.
</span><span class='line'>.</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div></p>

<h3>Start daemons</h3>

<pre><code>sudo service gmetad start
sudo service gmond start  
sudo service httpd start
</code></pre>

